# Versioning & Releases

## Semver
- Both packages follow strict semver. MAJOR (breaking), MINOR (features), PATCH (fixes).
- NPM and PyPI share the same version number.

## Changelog
- `CHANGELOG.md` at root. Every version: date, version, grouped changes (Added/Changed/Fixed/Removed).
- Generated from conventional commits.

## Releases
- Git tags (`v1.0.0`) trigger CI publish. Never publish from local. Test artifact before announcing.
